[The incubation period between the meal and the onset of symptoms is not stated, and no symptom complex is provided. The goat meat is implicated, but it is not known what else was ingested. With a case fatality of rate of almost 50%, a poisoning rather than an infection or biological intoxication is likely to be the cause. - Mod.LL

